cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper is about salient object detection using deep learning and graphical models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves message-passing and joint end-to-end model training, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and the evaluation on image datasets suggest that the paper may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the use of graphical models and joint refinement may also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
